quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  32,1,Alif-Lâm-Mîm
  32,2,"(Esi) sisityhilelo seNcwadi ekungekho ntandabuzo ngayo, sivela kwiNkosi yamaphakade"
  32,3,"Okanye mhlawumbi bathi: “UMuhammad Uyiqambe ngokwakhe?” Ukusuka apho yona iyinyaniso evela eNkosini yakho, khon’ukuze ulumkise abantu abangazanga baba naMlumkisi uzayo (kubo) ngaphambili kunawe, ukuze bakhokeleleke"
  32,4,NguAllâh Owadala amazulu nomhlaba nako konke okuphakathikwawongeentsukuezintandathu;WazaWazimisa ngentla kweTrone. Nina ngaphandle kwaKhe aninamkhuseli okanye umthetheleli; ngoko ke aniyi kukhumbuzeka na
  32,5,Yena Ucwangcisa yonke into esemazulwini nasemhlabeni; ukanti iza kuphinda inyukele kuYe ngeMini ebude bayo buyiminyaka eliwaka yaleyo niyibalayo
  32,6,"LoWo nguMazi wokungabonwayo, nongqinelwayo, uSobunganga, uSozinceba"
  32,7,Yena Wafezekisa zonke izinto Awazidalayo Waza Wayila indalo yomntu ngodongwe
  32,8,Waza Wenza ukwanda kwakhe ngolwelo olunyanyekayo (imbewu yomntu)
  32,9,"Wambumba ngomlinganiselo ofanelekileyo, Wamphefumlela umoya wobomi, Wanenzela ukuva nokubona nentliziyo (ingqiqo); kuncinane enibulela ngako"
  32,10,"Kananjalo bathi: “Sisakuba sele sinyamalele emhlabeni, ingaba ngenene siza (kuphinda sidalwe) sibe kwindalo entsha?” Eneneni bona kwindibano yabo neNkosi yabo abakholwa"
  32,11,"Yithi: “Ingelosi yokufa yona nibekwe phantsi kohoyo lwayo, iza kunithatha. Ke kaloku eNkosini yenu kulapho niza kubuyiselwa khona.”"